  "summary": {
    "as": "Passed House",
    "asOf": "2019-12-03",
    "date": "2020-04-22T15:55:57Z",
    "text": "This bill modifies the eligibility criteria for an elderly offender to qualify for early release from prison and placement in home detention.\n\nSpecifically, it reduces the amount of a prison term an elderly offender must serve by the amount of good time credits earned by the offender."
